  3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439277903037*^9}, {
  3.6264401828552628`*^9, 3.6264401857929173`*^9}, {3.626440791984539*^9, 
  3.626440804219549*^9}, {3.6264411054407115`*^9, 3.6264411068001337`*^9}, {
  3.626615603518798*^9, 3.6266156081284084`*^9}, {3.847186289939029*^9, 
  3.8471862929390554`*^9}, {3.8475326936198416`*^9, 3.8475326963556194`*^9}, {
  3.847552454660143*^9, 3.8475524568347383`*^9}},
 FontFamily->
  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"adc111a7-901d-4ab0-9147-445e24cabcd3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "(i) Every eigenvalue of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0d3aacde-d9a5-4f3d-8908-ae4f791933d8"],
 " is real."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.625576018846874*^9, 3.625576024206529*^9}, {
  3.6255760570961037`*^9, 3.6255760582524166`*^9}, {3.626439145126526*^9, 
  3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439430851683*^9}, {
  3.626440810923021*^9, 3.626440854597165*^9}},
 FontFamily->
  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"ea835446-dc65-44c9-a1fb-223fe59f1ba8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "(ii) The characteristic polynomial of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "86cdae77-bee0-4927-af00-1f0fdfb9a756"],
 " splits over ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["\[DoubleStruckCapitalR]", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e0a432e0-cf9d-46e4-8c94-0c036e570fb4"],
 ".  "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.625576018846874*^9, 3.625576024206529*^9}, {
  3.6255760570961037`*^9, 3.6255760582524166`*^9}, {3.626439145126526*^9, 
  3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439430851683*^9}, {
  3.626440810923021*^9, 3.6264408752232013`*^9}, {3.6264409610401907`*^9, 
  3.62644096361845*^9}, {3.6264410325619116`*^9, 3.6264410325775175`*^9}},
 FontFamily->
  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"94335450-586b-47d3-b7b0-8de673757991"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[StyleBox["PROOF:",
 FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
 FontColor->RGBColor[
  0., 0.5019607843137255, 0.5019607843137255]]], "Subsubsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.625576018846874*^9, 3.625576024206529*^9}, {
  3.6255760570961037`*^9, 3.6255760582524166`*^9}, {3.626439145126526*^9, 
  3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439430851683*^9}, {
  3.626440810923021*^9, 3.6264408752232013`*^9}, {3.6264409610401907`*^9, 
  3.62644096361845*^9}, {3.6264410325619116`*^9, 3.6264410333744683`*^9}, {
  3.6266127685321875`*^9, 3.6266127832048225`*^9}, {3.6266160427852783`*^9, 
  3.626616042800875*^9}},
 FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
 FontSize->12,ExpressionUUID->"425686b3-b125-4a09-b68e-b8325923c285"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Since ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6aca652f-18e9-43b4-b51e-2dc6f938f381"],
 " is also normal, we know that there is an orthogonal basis of eigenvectors \
and hence ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b19d0a80-c256-4777-9628-3b26dd7cc04b"],
 " is diagonalizable. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.878990426077155*^9, {3.878990489265103*^9, 3.878990648336321*^9}, {
   3.9107109868455067`*^9, 
   3.910711011576293*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0ac567d3-09f4-4da4-af45-\
d42a8cfba720"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Additionally we know ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"[", "T", "]"}], "\[Beta]"], "*"], "=", 
    SubscriptBox[
     RowBox[{"[", "T", "]"}], "\[Beta]"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "2e40935b-5032-4f9a-b2e6-2bb02d3f6dd2"],
 " and since the eigenvalues occur on the diagonal of this matrix, in order \
for it to equal its conjugate transpose the diagonal elements (eigenvalues) \
must be real. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.878990426077155*^9, {3.878990489265103*^9, 3.878990648336321*^9}, {
   3.9107109881920815`*^9, 
   3.9107109945275373`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7842e546-5149-4220-8d13-\
779019df0767"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Moreover, the characteristic polynomial is the characteristic polynomial of \
this matrix, which is already split into linear factors over ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["\[DoubleStruckCapitalR]", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "51070360-62ae-4023-ae91-f1c63d49e38d"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.878990426077155*^9, {3.878990489265103*^9, 3.878990648336321*^9}, 
   3.9107109881920815`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"bae95475-862a-4043-b555-\
bfe233221160"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Theorem: ",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0.5, 0.5]],
 " "
}], "Subsubsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.625576018846874*^9, 3.625576024206529*^9}, {
   3.6255760570961037`*^9, 3.6255760582524166`*^9}, {3.626439145126526*^9, 
   3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439430851683*^9}, {
   3.626440810923021*^9, 3.6264408752232013`*^9}, {3.6264409610401907`*^9, 
   3.62644096361845*^9}, {3.6264410325619116`*^9, 3.6264410972527637`*^9}, {
   3.6266127232954273`*^9, 3.6266127236079445`*^9}, {3.626615339980116*^9, 
   3.626615340558281*^9}, 3.626616369211627*^9, {3.626616455224142*^9, 
   3.6266164629705343`*^9}, {3.626616617871415*^9, 3.626616617871415*^9}, 
   3.8471863937286797`*^9},
 FontFamily->"Times New Roman",
 FontSize->12,ExpressionUUID->"c21f809c-631d-46b3-a8b2-d7bcae42869b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "893bd567-6bf1-4b1a-b256-4e7e8715eb13"],
 " is a self-adjoint (symmetric) operator on a finite dimensional ",
 StyleBox["real ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "vector space ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4d294170-e45f-426a-b07d-e67b8067dcc4"],
 " if and only if  there is an orthogonal basis for ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4943ce5d-8230-420e-83c5-fbc68a0cd0ea"],
 " consisting of eigenvectors of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "354db778-879e-47d5-ad59-075be2559f52"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.625576018846874*^9, 3.625576024206529*^9}, {
   3.6255760570961037`*^9, 3.6255760582524166`*^9}, {3.626439145126526*^9, 
   3.626439208399403*^9}, {3.6264392756528873`*^9, 3.626439430851683*^9}, {
   3.626440810923021*^9, 3.6264408752232013`*^9}, {3.6264409610401907`*^9, 
   3.62644096361845*^9}, {3.6264410325619116`*^9, 3.6264410972527637`*^9}, {
   3.6266127232954273`*^9, 3.6266127236079445`*^9}, {3.626615339980116*^9, 
   3.626615340558281*^9}, 3.626616369211627*^9, {3.626616455224142*^9, 
   3.6266164629705343`*^9}, {3.626616617871415*^9, 3.626616617871415*^9}, 
   3.847186426104825*^9, {3.8475327788596516`*^9, 3.847532810676116*^9}},
 FontFamily->
  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"392be040-2379-463e-9548-60fc29f6f066"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

